{"type":"text","timestamp":1775825679131,"sessionID":"ses_2888cfa99ffeQ6pxpb8jA6eZSi","part":{"id":"prt_d7774d5360017AqoyB5huRi92m","messageID":"msg_d7773f44d001PKqlCmtT6ysvjx","sessionID":"ses_2888cfa99ffeQ6pxpb8jA6eZSi","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the codebase against the AR-008 task清单 and delta-spec, here is the summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-008 Archive Summary\n\n### Completed\n\n**Core Implementation (all source code):**\n- `SandboxInfo` extended with `LastActivityAt` field; `SandboxStatusResponse`/`SandboxListItem` extended with `LastActivityAt`, `TimeToIdle`, `IsIdle`\n- GC constants defined: `DefaultIdleTimeout` (15m), `MaxOrphanScanLimit` (100), cleanup reasons (`ttl_expired`, `idle`, `orphan_cr`, `ghost_entry`)\n- `MetricsRecorder` interface extended with 4 GC methods; `PrometheusMetricsRecorder` fully implemented with nil-safety\n- `LifecycleManager` extended with `defaultIdleTimeout` and `metricsRecorder` fields; constructor applies defaults\n- All `log.Printf` replaced with `slog` structured logging in `sandbox_lifecycle.go`\n- `isExpired` verified (ExpiresAt / CreatedAt+TTL logic)\n- `isIdleExpired` implemented (zero-value safe, status check, timeout comparison)\n- `deleteSandbox` enhanced with `reason` parameter; ghost_entry auto-detection when CR already deleted; metrics + structured logging\n- `cleanupExpiredSandboxes` enhanced: dual-pass TTL + idle cleanup with separate counters\n- `cleanupOrphanCRs` implemented: scans AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter CRs, validates against Store, respects `MaxOrphanScanLimit`\n- `cleanupGhostEntries` implemented: validates Store entries against K8s CR existence, cleans orphaned entries\n- `runGCCycle` orchestrates all subtasks in order (TTL/idle → orphan → ghost) with error isolation (one failure doesn't block others)\n- `calculateTimeToIdle` helper implemented\n- API endpoints (`GetSandboxStatus`, `ListSandboxes`, `ExtendSandboxTTL`) populate new response fields; `GetSandboxStatus`/`ExtendSandboxTTL` refresh `LastActivityAt`\n- `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations` / `extractIdleTimeoutFromCR` helper functions implemented\n\n**Existing Tests (pre-AR-008, still passing):**\n- Basic LifecycleManager constructor, isExpired, Start/Stop idempotency\n- ExtendTTLRequest validation\n- GetSandboxStatus, ListSandboxes, ExtendSandboxTTL endpoint tests\n- JSON serialization tests\n- One cleanupExpiredSandboxes test (TTL-only scenario)\n\n---\n\n### Deferred / Not Yet Implemented\n\n**Unit Tests (T-005, T-010, T-012, T-014, T-016, T-018, T-020, T-024, T-026):**\n- GC metrics unit tests (`IncGCCleanupTotal`, `ObserveGCCleanupDuration`, etc.)\n- `isIdleExpired` unit tests (4 scenarios)\n- `deleteSandbox` enhanced unit tests (5 scenarios including ghost_entry, metrics recording)\n- `cleanupExpiredSandboxes` enhanced tests (idle timeout scenarios, mixed expired+idle)\n- `cleanupOrphanCRs` unit tests (7 scenarios including max limit, list failure, delete failure)\n- `cleanupGhostEntries` unit tests (6 scenarios)\n- GC cycle integration tests (ticker trigger, Stop exit, idempotent Start/Stop, error isolation, cycle metrics)\n- `LastActivityAt` refresh unit tests (create, status check, TTL extend, reconciler pod)\n- `TimeToIdle`/`IsIdle` calculation unit tests\n\n**LastActivityAt Refresh Gaps (T-021, T-023):**\n- `sandbox_create.go`: `LastActivityAt` is **not** set on `StoreSandbox` or `UpdateSandbox` during sandbox creation (both AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter paths)\n- `reconciler/pod.go`: `LastActivityAt` is **not** refreshed on Pod IP update\n\n**Spec Deviation:**\n- `cleanupExpiredSandboxes` uses `m.defaultIdleTimeout` for all sandboxes; does **not** read per-sandbox `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` annotation from CR as specified in delta-spec Requirement scenarios\n\n**Verification Gate (T-027):**\n- Full test suite execution, coverage measurement (≥80% line coverage, T/C > 0.4), `-race` detector, `log.Printf` grep verification not yet run","time":{"start":1775825679128,"end":1775825679128}}}
